name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Switzerland Points of Interest, Switzerland, 2008
description: This data set shows points of interest in Switzerland. Features included in this data set include, libraries, post offices, places of worship, parking, restaurants, cafes, fuel, parking, police, theaters, cinemas, prisons, universities, camp sites and other public places. there are almost 5,000 points of interest included.
